  "description": {
    "zh": "Victor正在考虑派他的一些人进入塔科夫清理走私者，可能也要除掉他们，有趣的资源利用方式，嗯。总之他问我是否认识可以调试他的枪的人，我想我知道该问谁这个问题。他给了我几把SR-2M冲锋枪和一些配套的手枪，还给了我一份必须满足的标准清单。你觉得你能搞定吗？\n\nSR-1MP 要求：\n - 耐久度高于75%\n - 弹匣容量18发或更多\n - 一个抑制器\n - Zenit Klesch-2P战术灯带激光\n\nSR-2M 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于220\n - 重量小于2.9公斤\n - 人机工效65或更高\n - 耐久度高于75%\n - 弹匣容量30发或更多\n - 瞄准距离200米或更远\n - SR-2M手枪握把（黑色）\n - SR-2M聚合物护木（黑色）\n - Zenit Klesch-2P战术灯带激光",
    "en": "Victor was thinking about sending out a few of his guys into Tarkov to clean up after the smugglers and probably to get rid of them aswell, interesting use of resources, hmm. Anyway he asked me if I know someone that could tune his guns, and I think I know the right person to ask this question. He gave me a few SR-2M submachineguns and some pistols to go along with them, also gave me a list of standards that have to be met. You think you can manage that?\n\nSR-1MP Requirements :\n - Durability higher than 75 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 18 or more\n - A Suppressor\n - Zenit Klesch-2P Flashlight with Laser\n\nSR-2M Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 220\n - Weight less than 2.9 KG\n - Ergonomics 65 or higher\n - Durability higher than 75 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 30 or more\n - Sighting Range of 200 Meters or more\n - SR-2M Pistol Grip ( Black )\n - SR-2M Polymer Handguard ( Black )\n - Zenit Klesch-2P Flashlight with Laser"
  },
